00:16:44.880 --> 00:16:50.970
Raksit: in terms of f0, they have a larger have f0 difference. The blue curves are farther apart than the red curves are.

121
00:16:52.020 --> 00:16:59.460
Raksit: Now, there aren't enough speakers yet for a cross section with away long. The cells basically end up getting really small, there are very small numbers in each cell

